 effective\nspin for primordial binaries, and with maximal effective spin for dynamical\nbinaries.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 4 Feb 2018 21:00:19 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 11 Sep 2018 18:06:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-09-13"}
