g reduction in $t_f$ when shortcuts are\npresent, their presence by itself is not sufficient to trigger a superdiffusive\nbehavior.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 4 Feb 2018 21:37:28 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 8 Jun 2018 08:56:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-06-11"}
